# Network Traffic Analysis (DNS, HTTP & ICMP)

## 🎯 Objective
To capture and analyze different types of network traffic (DNS, HTTP, and ICMP) using Wireshark in a Kali Linux virtual environment. The goal was to understand how devices communicate over a network and how websites are resolved and accessed.

---

## 🛠 Tools Used
- Kali Linux
- Wireshark
- VirtualBox
- Terminal (ping, curl commands)

---

